declarations.comments:
CBOR decoding transform stream

Accepts unencoded `Buffer` chunks, and transforms them
to JS values.
declarations.title: CBORDecoder

declarations.comments: `data` event. Emitted when a CSV record has been parsed.
declarations.title: dataH

declarations.comments:
Create a raw Transform stream that accepts chunks of `Array String`,
and transforms them into string CSV rows.

Requires an ordered array of column names.
declarations.title: make

declarations.comments: Convert the raw stream to a typed ObjectStream
declarations.title: toObjectStream

declarations.comments:
Write a record to a CSVStringifier.

The record will be emitted on the `Readable` end
of the stream as a string chunk.
declarations.title: write

declarations.comments:
Transforms buffer chunks of a CBOR file to parsed values
of type `a`.
declarations.title: decode

declarations.comments: Encode purescript values as CBOR buffers
declarations.title: encode
